</P>
<P>
 * Course was closed six months for irrigation improvements 
</P>
<P>
 Note: Revenue and profit/loss figures are for fiscal year 1993 
</P>
<P>
 SOURCES: City of Los Angeles, Los Angeles County, the Southern California 
Public Links Golf Assn. and the Los Angeles Municipal Golf Assn.  
</P>
