<TEXT>
<P>
 A 16-year-old boy and a second man were shot early Sunday at a residence in 
the 300 block of Coffman Street, and three people were arrested in the 
incident, police said. 
</P>
<P>
 According to police, officers responding to a report of shots fired just after 
midnight found a 16-year-old boy who had been wounded several times in the 
